### **ğŸ”¹ Benefits of AWS Organizations**
âœ” **Cost Optimization** â€“ Single consolidated billing reduces overhead.  
âœ” **Improved Security** â€“ SCPs enforce policies across accounts.  
âœ” **Better Management** â€“ Easier to handle multiple teams/projects.  

