âœ” **AWS Accounts** â€“ Separate environments for managing resources and billing.  
âœ” **AWS Organizations** â€“ A management tool for multiple AWS accounts with **centralized billing** and **policy control**.  
âœ” **Service Control Policies (SCPs)** â€“ Restrict actions across AWS accounts.  

